videos.description: Emmett Narr sends his defender to the court with a cross over and hits the lay-in to give him an early 10 points against Georgia.
videos.headline: Saint Mary's Naar crosses defender, hits layup

videos.description: Emmett Naar misses a layup, Jock Landale is there for the rebound and lay-in before the half.
videos.headline: Saint Mary's Landale answers with putback basket

videos.description: Emmett Naar passes the ball to Evan Fitzner who makes his fourth 3-ball of the game.
videos.headline: Fitzner drains fourth 3-pointer for Saint Mary's

videos.description: Derek Ogbeide blocks Emmett Naar's layup attempt, the Bulldogs' 6th blocked shot against Saint Mary's.
videos.headline: Georgia's Ogbeide denies Naar's shot

videos.description: Tyree Crump makes a long jumper to add to the Bulldogs' lead early in the second half.
videos.headline: Georgia extends lead with Crump 3-pointer

videos.description: Emmett Naar gets the ball to Jock Landale who gets an easy dunk forcing Georgia to call a timeout.
videos.headline: Saint Mary's takes momentum with Landale dunk

videos.description: Georgia's William Jackson II drives in and makes the layup to send the game to overtime.
videos.headline: Jackson layup forces overtime against Saint Mary's
